head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths WEBSTER, ELIZABETH WYLIE

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths WEBSTER, ELIZABETH WYLIE

block.p: WEBSTER-Elizabeth Wylie. 92, of Meadow Lakes, Hightstown, NJ on September 1, 2000. Graduate of Vassar College and served on the Board of the YWCA of NYC. Wife of the late James H. Case, Jr. and the late Bethuel M. Webster. Survived by three daughters, Elizabeth Case Mills, Susan C. Hyde and Penelope C. Davis; three stepdaughters, 11 grandchildren and 13 great-grandchildren. Services will be private. For more information, A.S. Cole Funeral Home.
